      "start_time": 0.49,
      "recording_attendee_id": "789f7d0a-78bc-4885-8a40-b9d0ffd5eb82",
      "order_number": 1,
      "text": "Thank you for calling about, how can I help you?"
    },
    {
      "id": "17d7ae2c-28b1-4574-96c1-01089a7c511f",
      "recording_id": "434287ee-6fb7-450e-99a9-9b0646c68a00",
      "end_time": 4.61,
      "start_time": 2.6,
      "recording_attendee_id": "268fe315-3124-4f63-bb60-5fa98540e8c6",
      "order_number": 2,
      "text": "Hi, is Abby smith available?"
    },
    {
      "id": "17d7ae2c-28b1-4574-96c1-01089a7c511f",
      "recording_id": "434287ee-6fb7-450e-99a9-9b0646c68a00",
      "end_time": 5.83,
      "start_time": 4.64,
      "recording_attendee_id": "789f7d0a-78bc-4885-8a40-b9d0ffd5eb82",
      "order_number": 3,
      "text": "May I ask who's calling?"
    },
    {
      "id": "17d7ae2c-28b1-4574-96c1-01089a7c511f",
      "recording_id": "434287ee-6fb7-450e-99a9-9b0646c68a00",
      "end_time": 8.5,
      "start_time": 5.87,
      "recording_attendee_id": "268fe315-3124-4f63-bb60-5fa98540e8c6",
      "order_number": 4,
      "text": "Yeah, it's Brandon calling with rentable."
    },
    {
      "id": "17d7ae2c-28b1-4574-96c1-01089a7c511f",
      "recording_id": "434287ee-6fb7-450e-99a9-9b0646c68a00",
      "end_time": 41.03,
      "start_time": 8.85,
      "recording_attendee_id": "789f7d0a-78bc-4885-8a40-b9d0ffd5eb82",
      "order_number": 5,
      "text": "Rentable? Alright, hold on, let me see if she's available. Thank you for calling added realty Hampton roads, most established real estate company, with a history of proven success and a vision for your future. Did you know you can view and receive current listings from our website. This is Abby May I help you?"
    },
    {
      "id": "17d7ae2c-28b1-4574-96c1-01089a7c511f",
      "recording_id": "434287ee-6fb7-450e-99a9-9b0646c68a00",
      "end_time": 45.82,
      "start_time": 41.56,
      "recording_attendee_id": "268fe315-3124-4f63-bb60-5fa98540e8c6",
      "order_number": 6,
      "text": "Hey, good afternoon, Abby, It's Brandon calling with rentable. How are you doing today?"
    },
    {
      "id": "17d7ae2c-28b1-4574-96c1-01089a7c511f",
      "recording_id": "434287ee-6fb7-450e-99a9-9b0646c68a00",
      "end_time": 47.11,
      "start_time": 45.82,
      "recording_attendee_id": "789f7d0a-78bc-4885-8a40-b9d0ffd5eb82",
      "order_number": 7,
      "text": "I'm fine, how are you?"
    },
    {
      "id": "17d7ae2c-28b1-4574-96c1-01089a7c511f",
      "recording_id": "434287ee-6fb7-450e-99a9-9b0646c68a00",
      "end_time": 71.01,
      "start_time": 47.2,
      "recording_attendee_id": "268fe315-3124-4f63-bb60-5fa98540e8c6",
      "order_number": 8,
      "text": "I'm good. I'm good. Uh wanted to wanted to reach out, I actually just um called over to River Acres and I was informed that you would be the best person to reach out to and wanted to see how things are going for you guys in regards to your marketing, your advertising and and how your current internet listings are are performing right now for you?"
    },
    {
      "id": "17d7ae2c-28b1-4574-96c1-01089a7c511f",
      "recording_id": "434287ee-6fb7-450e-99a9-9b0646c68a00",
      "end_time": 73.97,
      "start_time": 71.36,
      "recording_attendee_id": "789f7d0a-78bc-4885-8a40-b9d0ffd5eb82",
      "order_number": 9,
      "text": "Uh they're doing fine and we're at full capacity so."
    },
    {
      "id": "17d7ae2c-28b1-4574-96c1-01089a7c511f",
      "recording_id": "434287ee-6fb7-450e-99a9-9b0646c68a00",
      "end_time": 83.81,
      "start_time": 73.87,
      "recording_attendee_id": "268fe315-3124-4f63-bb60-5fa98540e8c6",
      "order_number": 10,
      "text": "Awesome, awesome. Um Well in that case, um I guess how many properties do you guys have right now that are that are out there?"
    },
    {
      "id": "17d7ae2c-28b1-4574-96c1-01089a7c511f",
      "recording_id": "434287ee-6fb7-450e-99a9-9b0646c68a00",
      "end_time": 90.82,
      "start_time": 85.38,
      "recording_attendee_id": "789f7d0a-78bc-4885-8a40-b9d0ffd5eb82",
      "order_number": 11,
      "text": "Oh gosh. You know what I do the marketing for them, but I'm not in charge of the management side of the house so"
    },
    {
      "id": "17d7ae2c-28b1-4574-96c1-01089a7c511f",
      "recording_id": "434287ee-6fb7-450e-99a9-9b0646c68a00",
